The,Open,Food,Facts,API,provides,access,to,data,and,information,on,food,products,from,around,the,world,Access,extensive,data,on,product,ingredients,nutrition,facts,allergens,additives,and,search,filter,by,product,or,brand,This,free,and,open,API,is,JSON,based,and,accessed,over,HTTP,using,product,barcode,information,Developers,should,note,that,the,API,is,still,experimental,and,may,change,The,authors,ask,that,you,join,the,API,mailing,list,to,be,kept,abreast,of,changes,and,updates,Join,the,mailing,list,at,api,subscribe,openfoodfacts,org